# Project Tracking Template - Git Ignore Rules

# Optional: Add this entire directory to your project's .gitignore if you want
# to keep project tracking private or local to development team

# Remove any of these rules as needed for your project

# Session artifacts that might contain sensitive information
sessions/SESSION_*_DRAFT.md
sessions/SESSION_*_PRIVATE.md

# Temporary files created during planning
*.tmp
*.draft
*_backup.json

# Personal notes (team members might create these)
PERSONAL_NOTES.md
TODO_PERSONAL.md

# Tool-generated files (if using automated tools)
reports/
dashboards/
exports/

# IDE or editor specific files
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
*~

# OS generated files
.DS_Store
.DS_Store?
._*
.Spotlight-V100
.Trashes
ehthumbs.db
Thumbs.db

# Node modules if using JS-based validation tools
node_modules/

# Python cache if using Python-based tools
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class

# Logs from automated tools
*.log
logs/